amped with your personal stamp. Take care not to mix up stamps and to leave the caches stamp in the cache! Frequently letterboxes can be found without GPS, maybe with a compass and paces from a location - add the \"without GPS\" attribute for those.','2010-09-12 22:54:24'),(1549,'EN','The cache is located within a dangerous area. Use this attribute to mark non-obvious dangers, like high-traffic roads, steep ground or falling rocks. Security measures should be taken or the cache be omitted, especially when geocaching with children, large groups or at unfavourable weather conditions.','2010-09-12 22:53:29'),(1550,'EN','Active railway nearby','2010-09-12 23:13:51'),(1551,'EN','Cliff / Rocks','2010-09-12 23:17:29'),(1552,'EN','Hunting','2010-09-12 23:17:34'),(1553,'EN','Thorns','2010-09-12 23:17:39'),(1554,'EN','Ticks','2010-09-12 23:17:17'),(1555,'EN','Abandoned mines','2010-09-12 23:17:25'),(1556,'EN','Poisonous plants','2010-09-12 23:17:03'),(1557,'EN','Dangerous animals','2010-09-12 23:16:58'),(1558,'EN','Parking area nearby','2010-09-12 23:17:11'),(1559,'EN','Public transportation','2010-09-12 23:17:07'),(1560,'EN','Drinking water nearby','2010-09-12 23:16:49'),(1561,'EN','Public restrooms nearby','2010-09-12 23:16:54'),(1562,'EN','Public phone nearby','2010-09-12 23:16:23'),(1563,'EN','First aid available','2010-09-12 23:16:19'),(1564,'EN','Near the parking area','2010-09-12 23:16:41'),(1565,'EN','Long walk','2010-09-12 23:16:27'),(1566,'EN','Swamp, marsh or wading','2010-09-12 23:16:36'),(1567,'EN','Hilly area','2010-09-12 23:16:46'),(1568,'EN','Some climbing (no gear needed)','2010-09-12 23:15:51'),(1569,'EN','Swimming required','2010-09-12 23:15:28'),(1570,'EN','Point of interest','2010-09-12 23:16:15'),(1571,'EN','Moving target','2010-09-12 23:15:56'),(1572,'EN','Webcam','2010-09-12 23:15:32'),(1573,'EN','Wihin enclosed rooms (caves, buildings etc.)','2010-09-12 23:16:05'),(1575,'EN','Without GPS (letterboxes, cistes, compass juggling ...)','2010-09-12 23:15:0